{"tid":665864,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［數學問題］Thanos 幾多年後要啪多次手指？","createTime":"2018-05-15T10:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T06:43:56.000Z","uid":12633,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"003c4ec0d635d32da4910f3524347435936509ac","tid":665864,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"假設全世界有人口 k，而Thanos殺左一半人口；<br />\n咁要幾多年，人口會由 「k既一半 」升返去 k?<br />\n<br />\n1. 而家既birth rate係 0.02，姐係每年1000人入面會生20個人<br />\n<br />\n2. 所以 k = (k/2) x (1.02^n)<br />\nn = year required<br />\n<br />\n3. 最後計到 n=35，姐係35年後，Thanos又要啪多次手指<br />\n<br />\n呢條數係half-life既掉轉版。<br />\n有無計錯？"},{"pid":"a63f9a0d3889966b40e9d0c6c762c0de8395f06c","tid":665864,"uid":150881,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:43:45.000Z","msg":"唔知"},{"pid":"c4c02f3e499fceaea9e9ef4eba7ade690a4881c5","tid":665864,"uid":79953,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"thanos係random殺一半<br />\n無生育能力嘅點計"},{"pid":"d2960202241df45c1b247988e5b493e1b559eaf7","tid":665864,"uid":168540,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:46:56.000Z","msg":"就咁計就係, 如果引入埋有資源 同資源消耗/補充速率就好玩好多"},{"pid":"ec1d5ff4bf3e684bd40385ddf4f8d546cc26bcd9","tid":665864,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"出生率唔係固定，每10年啪一次差不多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442e6bfc4c838a9b166fa291b2cc5cc5c7f9762e","tid":665864,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"Thanos用time stone 直接time travel去到35年後啪手指, 唔需要等待"},{"pid":"720d86b0a663cde5a46cce135bdaf35a7bcd4a15","tid":665864,"uid":6674,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"GS?"},{"pid":"a8b2683d994dc449f430ae54791192b3fe03b83e","tid":665864,"uid":48104,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-1